Package de.dfki.oms.webapp

Classes handling the appearance and functionality of the web interface.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HTMLData
    A helper class to convert data from different sources and to HTML documents.
    OMM_HTML_Converter
    Helper class that converts OMS elements to HTML.
    OMSHandler
    A handler for HTTP requests to the OMS' "/web" and "/query" interfaces.
    OMSOMMHandler
    A handler for operations on the OMS issued via HTTP requests.
    RotatingTextTile
    A Tile with additional alternative text.
    Tile
    A tile to be used in the web interface of the OMS.
    TileStructure
    A grid of tiles used to build a memory view on the OMS's web interface.
    Tools
    Helpful methods to retrieve often needed information or perform frequent tasks.
